```
---
title: "Advanced DAG-Based Ranking (ADR) Protocol for Blockchain Scalability"
year: 2023
main_author: "Tayyaba Noreen, Qiufen Xia, and Muhammad Zeeshan Haider"
main_contribution: "Advanced DAG-based Ranking (ADR) protocol using a reputation-driven ranking algorithm and a Session Control Protocol (SCP) to improve scalability, throughput, and node reliability in private blockchain environments."
