reference: "Nasir, M. H., Arshad, J., Khan, M. M., Fatima, M., Salah, K., & Jayaraman, R. (2022). Scalable blockchains — A systematic review. Future Generation Computer Systems, 126, 136–162."
doi: "https://doi.org/10.1016/j.future.2021.07.035"
